  }, " open source internship programs"), ". We seek out existing contributors who actively reflect the culture and principles of Layer5 to participate in these programs. Here are the Fall of 2021's open source interns.")), mdx("p", null, "Hear about their journeys and follow along this fall as they make waves in the Layer5 community."), mdx("h2", null, mdx(Link, {
